Rating: 3
This was a delicious and simple recipe. A perforated mold is actually not necessary. Just strain the mixture, wrapped in cheesecloth, over a bowl. Afterwards you can spread it into any mold you like. Also, sour cream in place of most of the heavy cream cuts through some of the heaviness. I will definately make this again.

