Rating: 3
Made this for V-day with flourless chocolate cake. Couldn't find a mold in time, so spread it over cheesecloth the night before, then froze it briefly to firm up enough to cut with heart-shaped mini cookie cutters. It worked really well and the serving size wound up being about 1/4 cup- perfect as accompaniment to cake. The raspberry sauce was delicious and made a beautiful presentation.

