Rating: 4
I was a little intimidated to try this one because it looked so involved. Truthfully, it's very impressive with very minimal effort. They set up beautifully, and my fiancee was stunned at the presentation. (Do use this sauce or some sort of berry puree--it really needs the color and the tartness.) These are actually much less effort than baking a cake, and your guests will be in awe...

